{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_3","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/bash -lc \"sed -n '1,240p' Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P5-P6-lite/RESULT.html\"","aggregated_output":"<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n  <title>SP-A.P5-P6-lite Result</title>\n  <style>\n    body { margin: 0; background: #f6f8fa; color: #17202a; font: 15px/1.55 -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif; }\n    main { max-width: 1120px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 32px 24px 56px; }\n    section { background: #fff; border: 1px solid #d8e0e7; border-radius: 8px; padding: 18px 20px; margin: 16px 0; }\n    h1 { margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 28px; }\n    h2 { margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 20px; }\n    h3 { margin: 16px 0 8px; font-size: 16px; }\n    table { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 14px; }\n    th, td { border: 1px solid #d8e0e7; padding: 8px 10px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; }\n    th { background: #eef3f7; }\n    code, pre { font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace; }\n    code { background: #edf3f7; border-radius: 4px; padding: 1px 4px; }\n    pre { overflow-x: auto; background: #111827; color: #f8fafc; border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px; }\n    .meta { color: #5d6875; }\n    .ok { color: #276749; font-weight: 700; }\n    .warn { color: #9a4a17; font-weight: 700; }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<main>\n  <header>\n    <h1>SP-A.P5-P6-lite - Load VoxTell Transformer Decoder Prefix</h1>\n    <p class=\"meta\">Repository: <code>/home/xiaoqingguo/Rongkun/code/Hyper-Tell</code>. Source plan: <code>Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html</code>.</p>\n    <p><strong>Recommendation:</strong> <span class=\"ok\">ready_for_review</span></p>\n  </header>\n\n  <section>\n    <h2>Task Summary</h2>\n    <p>Completed P5/P6-lite for the runtime HWD position/memory contract and prefix-only VoxTell transformer decoder initialization. P5 remains folded into P6-lite: there is no independent <code>pos_embed</code> stage, no <code>fixed_voxtell_192</code>, and no <code>pos_embed</code> state-dict loading path.</p>\n    <p>The previous review failures were addressed directly. The runtime position tensor is cast back to the selected memory dtype after autocast-sensitive trig operations, fixing the CUDA bfloat16 mismatch. <code>train.py</code> now accepts and uses <code>--amp-dtype</code> and <code>--grad-clip-norm</code>; the phase1 Slurm gate completed successfully.</p>\n  </section>\n\n  <section>\n    <h2>Files Changed</h2>\n    <table>\n      <thead><tr><th>File</th><th>Change</th></tr></thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr><td><code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py</code></td><td>Uses VoxTell HWD flatten order, validates runtime <code>pos</code>/<code>memory</code> shape, batch, dtype, device, and channel contract, casts generated positions to memory dtype, and implements strict prefix-only transformer decoder loading.</td></tr>\n        <tr><td><code>Body-Tell/train.py</code></td><td>Adds <code>--init-transformer-from-voxtell</code>, <code>--amp-dtype</code>, and <code>--grad-clip-norm</code>; loads prefix before optimizer construction; logs/stores init metadata in checkpoint config.</td></tr>\n        <tr><td><code>Body-Tell/scripts/audit_voxtell_alignment.py</code></td><td>Adds CPU <code>transformer_decoder.</code> prefix audit and HTML reporting.</td></tr>\n        <tr><td><code>Body-Tell/tests/test_model_shapes.py</code></td><td>Adds non-cubic HWD flatten coverage, CUDA bfloat16 position dtype smoke coverage, and prefix-loader filtering coverage.</td></tr>\n        <tr><td><code>Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P5-P6-lite/audit_voxtell_alignment.html</code></td><td>Regenerated HTML audit report.</td></tr>\n        <tr><td><code>Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P5-P6-lite/RESULT.html</code></td><td>This report.</td></tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n    <p clas