><td>0</td><td>4</td><td>0</td></tr>\\n<tr><td><code>project_text_embed</code></td><td>4</td><td>4</td><td>4</td></tr>\\n<tr><td><code>project_to_decoder_channels</code></td><td>0</td><td>20</td><td>0</td></tr>\\n<tr><td><code>project_visual_embed</code></td><td>4</td><td>0</td><td>0</td></tr>\\n<tr><td><code>transformer_decoder</code></td><td>110</td><td>110</td><td>110</td></tr></tbody></table>\\n    <p>Same-name compatible current Body-Tell keys: <code>114</code>; shape mismatches: <code>0</code>; checkpoint keys unexpected to current Body-Tell: <code>981</code>.</p>\\n  </section>\\n\\n  <section>\\n    <h2>P6 Whitelist Input</h2>\\n    <h3>Required exact skips</h3>\\n    <table><thead><tr><th>Pattern</th><th>Reason</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>pos_embed</code></td><td>Body-Tell current non-192^3 crop uses dynamic positional encoding.</td></tr></tbody></table>\\n    <h3>Conditional skips</h3>\\n    <table><thead><tr><th>Pattern</th><th>Reason</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>project_to_decoder_channels.[1-4].*, decoder.transpconvs.[1-4].*, decoder.seg_layers.*</code></td><td>only apply if loading a checkpoint generated from the VoxTellModel source default num_heads=1 into a Body-Tell num_heads=32 model</td></tr></tbody></table>\\n    <ul><li>checkpoint-derived num_heads matches Body-Tell current num_heads; do not skip project_to_decoder_channels.* or decoder mask-fusion keys for this reason</li></ul>\\n  </section>\\n\\n  <section>\\n    <h2>Machine-Readable Audit Payload</h2>\\n    <pre>{\\n  &quot;body&quot;: {\\n    &quot;config_path&quot;: &quot;/home/xiaoqingguo/Rongkun/code/Hyper-Tell/Body-Tell/configs/phase1_voxtell_body.yaml&quot;,\\n    &quot;encoder_channels&quot;: [\\n      32,\\n      64,\\n      128,\\n      256,\\n      320\\n    ],\\n    &quot;fused_stage_count_actual&quot;: 4,\\n    &quot;num_heads&quot;: 32,\\n    &quot;num_maskformer_stages_config&quot;: 5,\\n    &quot;projection_prefix&quot;: &quot;mask_projections&quot;,\\n    &