>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P4/RESULT.html:36:    <p>Renamed projection modules to VoxTell-compatible state-dict names, changed bottleneck token layout to VoxTell's <code>B,C,D,H,W -&gt; B,H,W,D,C -&gt; H*W*D,B,C</code> path, and added non-cubic shape coverage to catch D/H/W swaps.</p>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P4/RESULT.html:44:        <tr><td><code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py</code></td><td>Renamed <code>project_visual_embed</code> to <code>project_bottleneck_embed</code>, renamed <code>mask_projections</code> to <code>project_to_decoder_channels</code>, kept <code>num_heads=32</code>, and switched bottleneck memory flattening to H/W/D order.</td></tr>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P4/RESULT.html:45:        <tr><td><code>Body-Tell/tests/test_model_shapes.py</code></td><td>Added projection-name/state-dict checks, path-B projection dimension checks, and a non-cubic <code>32 x 64 x 96</code> forward test proving output axes stay <code>D,H,W</code>.</td></tr>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P4/RESULT.html:46:        <tr><td><code>Body-Tell/scripts/audit_voxtell_alignment.py</code></td><td>Updated current Body-Tell projection reporting to the new <code>project_to_decoder_channels</code> prefix.</td></tr>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P4/RESULT.html:48:        <tr><td><code>Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P4/audit_projection_after_p4.html</code></td><td>Generated HTML audit artifact showing aligned projection dimensions and P6 whitelist input.</td></tr>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P4/RESULT.html:64:    <h3>Projection / whitelist audit artifact</h3>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P4/RESULT.html:67:  --skip-state-dict-compare \\\\\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P4/RESULT.html:70:Body-Tell current: num_heads=32, fused projection stages=5\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P4/RESULT.html:71:project_to_decoder_channels outputs: [32, 2048, 4096, 8192, 10240]\\nBody-Tell